    <item>
      <title>文件显示，交易完成后拉里·埃里森将接管派拉蒙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/larry-ellison-will-control-paramount-after-deal-filing-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据监管文件显示，在由软件亿万富翁拉里·埃里森之子大卫·埃里森领导的财团完成对雷石东家族在哥伦比亚广播公司 (CBS) 母公司派拉蒙全球的收购后，该公司将由软件亿万富翁拉里·埃里森控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/larry-ellison-will-control-paramount-after-deal-filing-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:02:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行称英伟达股价暴跌为买入提供了诱人的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/nvidia-s-rout-makes-for-compelling-chance-to-buy-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行表示，人工智能宠儿英伟达公司近期面临阻力，但这种阻力使其估值显得颇具吸引力，为投资者提供了颇具吸引力的买入机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/nvidia-s-rout-makes-for-compelling-chance-to-buy-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班将在最严峻的选举考验前放弃预算紧缩政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/hungary-s-orban-to-ditch-austerity-before-toughest-election-test</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 准备在选举前撕毁其预算整合承诺，以刺激支出浪潮，而选举将成为他十多年来执政以来最艰难的一次选举。福林兑欧元的涨幅被抹去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/hungary-s-orban-to-ditch-austerity-before-toughest-election-test</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:38:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+ 暂停增加石油供应，以扭转油价下滑趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/opec-has-deal-to-pause-planned-oil-hike-for-2-months-delegate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OPEC+ 将石油供应增加推迟了两个月，但由于对脆弱需求的担忧，此举不足以扭转原油价格的大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/opec-has-deal-to-pause-planned-oil-hike-for-2-months-delegate</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:03:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
